  <!-- ============================
       WHAT THE PROCESS LOOKS LIKE
  ============================= -->
  <section class="svc-section svc-process">
    <div class="svc-section-inner svc-section-inner--centered">
      <div class="svc-section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Step by step</span>
        <h2>What the process looks like</h2>
        <p>Employment disputes can feel overwhelming. Here's what to expect when you work with us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-steps">

        <div class="svc-step">
          <div class="svc-step-num">01</div>
          <div class="svc-step-content">
            <h3>Free consultation</h3>
            <p>We start with a free, no obligation conversation to understand your situation and advise whether you have a viable case.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="svc-step">
          <div class="svc-step-num">02</div>
          <div class="svc-step-content">
            <h3>Raise the grievance</h3>
            <p>We prepare and send a formal personal grievance letter to your employer, clearly setting out the basis of your claim.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="svc-step">
          <div class="svc-step-num">03</div>
          <div class="svc-step-content">
            <h3>Employer response</h3>
            <p>Your employer has a chance to respond. We review their position and advise you on next steps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="svc-step">
          <div class="svc-step-num">04</div>
          <div class="svc-step-content">
            <h3>Mediation</h3>
            <p>A mediator from the Ministry of Business, Innovation and Employment facilitates a discussion between both parties. Most cases settle here.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="svc-step">
          <div class="svc-step-num">05</div>
          <div class="svc-step-content">
            <h3>Authority hearing</h3>
            <p>If mediation is unsuccessful, the case proceeds to the Employment Relations Authority for a formal determination.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="svc-step">
          <div class="svc-step-num">06</div>
          <div class="svc-step-content">
            <h3>Resolution</h3>
            <p>Whether through settlement or a formal decision, we work to achieve the best possible outcome for you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>